const helmet = require('helmet');
app.use(helmet());
```

### 2. Server binds to all interfaces by default (A05) — **Low**

`app.listen(3000, ...)` binds to `0.0.0.0`. In a container/shared host this exposes the service broadly.

**Fix:**
```js
const HOST = process.env.HOST || '127.0.0.1';
const PORT = parseInt(process.env.PORT, 10) || 3000;
