Express ships with defaults that leak the framework (`X-Powered-By: Express`) and no security-relevant headers (CSP, HSTS, `X-Content-Type-Options`, `Referrer-Policy`, etc.).

**Recommendation:** use `helmet` and disable the fingerprint header.

```js
const helmet = require('helmet');
app.disable('x-powered-by');
app.use(helmet());
```

