### 2. No security headers (OWASP A05: Security Misconfiguration)

Express ships with permissive defaults and sends an `X-Powered-By: Express` header that leaks the framework.

**Recommendation:** Add [`helmet`](https://helmetjs.github.io/) and disable the fingerprint header.
```js
const helmet = require('helmet');
app.disable('x-powered-by');
app.use(helmet());
