  res.json(users.map(u => ({ id: u.id, name: u.name }))); // no email
});
```

### 4. No CORS policy declared (Low) — OWASP A05
Default behavior is "no CORS," which is actually safe, but if a browser client ever consumes this, someone will reach for `cors()` with `origin: '*'`. Set an explicit allowlist up front.
