**Fix:**
```js
const helmet = require('helmet');
app.disable('x-powered-by');
app.use(helmet());
```

### 2. No rate limiting (OWASP A04: Insecure Design / A07) — High

`/users` and `/health` can be hit without any throttling. `/health` in particular is a cheap DoS amplifier for scrapers and benchmarking scripts.

**Fix:**
```js
const rateLimit = require('express-rate-limit');
app.use(rateLimit({
  windowMs: 60_000,        // 1 minute
  max: 100,                // 100 req/min/IP
  standardHeaders: true,
  legacyHeaders: false,
}));
